Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I forgot my English textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:02.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go borrow Kagami's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They already had English, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:05.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You should double-check everything the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa tends to forget stuff a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...Konata doesn't forget stuff like textbooks much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:24.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's because I'm surprisingly \Ndiligent about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:27.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Plus, I never take my textbooks home in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's not called being diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:35.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you can't review what we went over \Nin class without a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I never study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:41.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since you end up cramming the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:44.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But Kona-chan's good at putting \Noff stuff till the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:49.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That could be why I forget to do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You don't forget to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:53.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You just don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So show me your homework \Nfor Japanese this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:57.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Already at it again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki's in your class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ask her to show you her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How should I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san's such a nice person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...that it ends up being hard to ask her for anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's this sensation you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I get what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I still can't accept it.
