Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He was like it's okay, we can split up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:38.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but the other five of us had gotten one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and he was the odd one out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...which kinda left a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:46.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you've been in the same party for a\Nlong time, you wanna help each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So we all backed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, friends are a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:51.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So you were up all night playing online games again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kept playing after I logged off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What? She's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:09.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This girl crashed into me in the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then she suddenly grabbed \Nmy hand and took off running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I learned that she'd stolen some taiyaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and was on the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what any of this had to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:23.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I had no choice but to duck into\Na café to hide from the taiyaki baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So many potential comebacks...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a teacher!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a human being!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm down with a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I need to take a sick day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Too much gaming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The same trick won't work every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. You've got a summer cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Winter's over and the weather's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so stop being lazy and get to class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So she totally treated me like \Nthe boy who cried wolf yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It looks like my fever broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but my throat still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That means you breathe through your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:21.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can also breathe through your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but wouldn't you usually \Nbreathe through your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:26.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:30.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But Kona-chan breathes through \Nher mouth more than her nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:31.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:32.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:35.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If a virus enters through your mouth, \Nyou get a throat infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:39.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And if a virus enters through your nose, \Nyou get a nasal infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:44.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So people with sore throats probably had a higher chance of a virus entering through their throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is when we turn to Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't feel like doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,About your birthday party today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How about we hold it at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's so hot that I can't move a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're baking cookies right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:12.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa and other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't abbreviate me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san and Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:28.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And it isn't much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I have presents for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Matching earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I considered a number of options...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I had a hard time making up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And here are presents from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.09,0:06:52.90,ls_fo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,242)\frx18\fry358\frz14.83\fad(200,0)\shad0\fnFlat Brush Thin\b0\bord1\c&H322F31&}Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:52.90,ls_fo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,242)\blur0.5\frx18\fry358\frz14.83\fad(200,0)\shad0\fnFlat Brush Thin\b0\bord1\c&H322F31&}Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Brigade chief armband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:00.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why should I put this on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:04.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I figured it would fit you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It'll go better on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:06.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then what is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,To Heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It cost a fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wear it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't try to make both of us cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:19.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's barely any different from our uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If it's too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:23.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You could hold back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:35.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's cookies are always so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I baked them with her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kinda learned as I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Having heard that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...some of these cookies \Ndon't taste that good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Weird, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wonder if this is one of Kagami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Might as well eat the cake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:58.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagamin. Only labors industriously on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...isn't there always a fight over how to cut the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you cut a cake into a bunch of slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...how do you divide up the strawberries on top...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...or decide who gets the chocolate decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My older sisters all love chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:21.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't expect that from Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:29.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My strawberry's awfully small.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Do I have cake on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:53.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I just discovered another facet of Kagamin's charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You sound just like Shin-chan so stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's almost summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:03.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The beach, the pool, and summer festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are there any other usual events?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Summer is all about the annual celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The beginning of the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The one and only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That only applies to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is that like cricket?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Everyone has their own different thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like visiting relatives or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...do you have some kind of regular summer activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:36.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking a vacation overseas again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:37.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She said again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stupid bourgeois!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is that like yogurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You said that you started working at a costume café...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you need a good figure to pull that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:49.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:53.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've been lamenting my lack of a chest for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but then this game said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,"A flat chest is a status symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A rarity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And when you think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...there is a demand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Which means I'm valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:10.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know how a line from \Na game can fill her with confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'm okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We have a test coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Should you be gaming so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you would only use some \Nof that passion for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your grades would probably go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she's so easily influenced...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:32.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...wouldn't she become a genius if\Nsomeone released a game that promoted studying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's already stuff like Moe Drill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wazzup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of youth crime lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Whenever that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...all the neighbors say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He was such a nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I never would have imagined \Nthat he could do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:48.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:53.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That just means you can't \Njudge a person on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you ever commit a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I always figured she would do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's so hot that I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:15.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I really understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:19.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but you never feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.35,TS/EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,370.5)\frz350.973\shad0\bord0\blur0.5\fs70\fnPixel Operator SC\b0\c&H619572&}Hiiragi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hello, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Making progress on your studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was tidying up my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:45.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know how kinda get the urge to start\Ncleaning when you're feeling the pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:48.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's get a little studying done today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll take a thirty minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Time's already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just thirty more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:12.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thirty more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:22.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't Haruhi about to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They definitely cut corners with \Nthose long-winded Nagato scenes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Ya***** hasn't been very impressive recently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:41.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They're already flaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's already two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not going to happen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll go to sleep and wake up early to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If I wake up at five...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I can sleep three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:15.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I ended up killing time yesterday by\Nreading manga and watching anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds like something you would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:18.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You sure have some odd taste in manga and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You read manga aimed at boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and mainly play dating sims for men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:29.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My dad reads manga and plays games a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I was probably influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've been watching him from the side since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can understand the manga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but playing dating sims in front of your daughter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of father is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't your mom have anything to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...with both of you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't have a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She died when I was really little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So I'm always doing housework...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...which is why I'm way better than Kagami is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:01.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't say stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...when the mood isn't right for comebacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's also good at cooking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I would say that I'm good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:08.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder how good Miyuki-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:12.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She looks rich...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so maybe she's bad at housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cooking, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:22.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I only help out from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:25.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I'm not very skilled at housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh! Knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But Miyuki's.so good at everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...that it doesn't really feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:36.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can't just assume that \Nshe's bad when she says she's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then what about our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I heard that she lives by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but she looks like she could be a slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,These days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...ya can get by without knowing how ta cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ya got your convenience stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,About as well as your average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't make jokes that sound like they're true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa still has my dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Could I get my dictionary back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I-I was doing a little cleaning for a change of pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:19.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:30.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The people at work are trying to\Ncome up with a new menu for summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So you do stuff like that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And wait, did you give up on studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Spicy stuff's good when it's hot outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so how about super spicy ramen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:43.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Go with something you would usually find in a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:46.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then a super spicy parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Could you stop skipping the \Nthinking process when you respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:03.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't our school have swimming class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We have a pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:08.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm actually relieved by that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:09.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't open my eyes underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I can't really swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are your weaknesses always anything but?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The summer Comp Festival is finally about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:32.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is why I started working...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You bring so many fond memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why are you pulling out an ancient reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:40.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When the customers start getting excited with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:47.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...doesn't it feel like everyone's \Npumped up together for the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:51.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use some of that passion on academic endeavors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having trouble getting to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guess I'll read until I fall asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I happen to have some stuff I just bought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So much for falling asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I'm feeling really sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:30.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can understand turning off \Nyour phones around priority seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Because of pacemakers and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:37.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But why do they ban cell phone \Nuse for the whole train?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you'll disturb other people when you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:47.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Aren't trains already noisy \Nwith people talking anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That includes men and women of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you going to work at the temple\Nfor summer festivals like for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't work in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:03.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's getting to be that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Weren't you on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of all the studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I weighed myself yesterday, it was down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So I figured it'd be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And like, you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My weight already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...went all the way up in like the blink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause you let go and started snacking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And wasn't that a senryu?
