Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.12,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an1}I only ate a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an3}It's not like a kilo or two more or\Nless is going to affect how you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:52.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why do you get so excited \Nand depressed over every kilogram?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is why women are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to be a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Welcome to another episode of Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Has everyone been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:17.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira Kogami, always running at 120%!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:17.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nyoron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:18.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm the assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:23.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't interrupt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This isn't a kiddy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Learn the job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be dropped from this role?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:34.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Give it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:45.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We have big news for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:47.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Published in the November issue of Comptiq...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Project Fashionable Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:54.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've already received this many \Npostcards from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:54.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:59.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I think there was another \Nperson involved in that project...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the feedback!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:04.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like cowabunga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:08.07,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't think anyone's going to \Nunderstand a joke from the eighties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then I'll reveal the idea \NI've selected after extensive review.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is from a Miss Cherry in Satte, Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Project Fashionable Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:23.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san's pigtails look great on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What if Akira-san also wore pigtails?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:27.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Pigtails, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:28.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hair styling is a woman's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If I split it in two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...it might look lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No ifs or buts about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:43.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't it impossible with your hair length...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:47.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's not like long hair is always a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.49,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.28,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,It's gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It weighs a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:50.07,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,It's really gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.45,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Like if you just twitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a pain to maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And frankly, it isn't in fashion right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guys run their mouth off about \Nliking long hair on women...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:58.96,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:03.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but do they have any idea how much\Ntime, effort, and money it takes to maintain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:01.04,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're talking about yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:01.63,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.50,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're not in character anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.67,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're no longer Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:07.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And nobody ever notices your efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.63,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.42,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's already time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,As for what would Akira look like with pigtails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:18.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can find out more on our \Nhomepage or the radio show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hope to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Both hands will be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an3}I made a funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.98,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Then please look \Nforward to next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,By attitude, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep cutting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That upset about getting burned in the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No! Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I just figured nobody would recognize cowabunga now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:39.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:39.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:40.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:41.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why don't we start over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:42.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I heard they're holding an audition for Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is the first I've heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:46.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can try out if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:47.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Try out? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.47,ls_alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I'm actually him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:57.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can sing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:00.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,As long as it's an anime song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can sing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...in many different voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Singing anime songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:09.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...is all about staying true to the original song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:11.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:12.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna sing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:16.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The title was displayed earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:18.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I didn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, you don't know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess you aren't any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:29.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've heard this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:32.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Weren't you watching the series with me a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:33.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:35.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I still prefer the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you an old geezer or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:47.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:51.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sis is the best singer out of us sisters.
