Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:27.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:28.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:29.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Golden Week...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:33.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...was apparently derived from industry lingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:36.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...for the period when movie \Nticket sales are extremely high.
